      • decodeBase64Lwm2m

        public static java.util.List<?> decodeBase64Lwm2m(java.nio.ByteBuffer buffer,
                                                  EncodingType contentType)
                                           throws DecodingException
        Decodes a LWM2M sequence encoded in Base64 into a list of LWM2M objects for which the type is not yet known
        Parameters:
        buffer - sequence to decode
        contentType - content type of the sequence
        Returns:
        List of LWM2M objects (i.e. Object instance, Resource instance, Resource) or bytes if content type is not recognised as a valid LWM2M encoding (i.e. other than JSON or TLV)
        Throws:
        DecodingException - if an error occurred during parsing

      • decodeBase64Lwm2m

                                                      java.lang.Class<T> clazz,
                                                      EncodingType contentType)
                                               throws DecodingException
        Decodes a LWM2M sequence encoded in Base64 into a list of LWM2M objects of type T
        Type Parameters:
        T - type of LWM2M objects to expect
        Parameters:
        buffer - sequence to decode
        clazz - type of LWM2M objects (i.e. Object instance, Resource instance, Resource) expected in sequence
        contentType - content type of the sequence
        Returns:
        List of LWM2M objects of type T or null if content type is not recognised
        Throws:
        DecodingException - if an error occurred during parsing
